250
00:17:15,120 --> 00:17:19,019
When you look at each other, your eyes sparkle.

251
00:17:19,020 --> 00:17:21,630
Only a fool can't tell.

252
00:17:32,060 --> 00:17:34,110
It's nothing to like someone of the same sex.

253
00:17:34,110 --> 00:17:37,099
